Class AgencyBillMoneySetupFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.web.producer.agencybill.AgencyBillMoneySetupFactory

  • public class AgencyBillMoneySetupFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Factory class to create agency bill money received setups, either for new incoming monies/distributions, or for editing existing monies/distributions
